schools.name: Asa E Low Jr Intermediate School

data.description: Multiple offers, best and final due by 3pm on October 10th. Absolutely wonderful  home in sought after Mansfield ISD. This beautifully laid out, open concept home is move in ready. The kitchen is open to breakfast and living area and has a gas cook top and plenty of cabinet and counter space. The large master bedroom enjoys a master bath with separate shower, dual sinks, and a large walk in closet. There is office on the first floor that would also make a great nursery or playroom. Upstairs features 3 additional bedrooms, a bathroom and game room. Enjoy the amazing outdoor space with a gorgeous pool and spa. Perfect location, and is just minutes from schools, shopping and restaurants. Downstairs carpet is new.
